column5: Yea I will be there tomorrow and Sunday.
Nice I'll do my best to get up there tomorrow. What part are you heading to Live2fish?
Will have to be Sunday now,Will have to wait for a beaten trail or two.Will be pretty tough walking today in 12" plus snow on the lake.
Stuck at home till the plows come clean up the street.  i miss my 4X4
Lovin the 2 man clam flip hut u sold me Jose. Thanks man Landry

Tough day today, I have a feeling that storm put the fish into a not so excited mood, lol..   Although I did land my first whitefish of the year, also got checked by two COs!  Nice to see those boys out there checking licenses.
Good to hear Landry it was a great hut.  I'm now waiting on my new eskimo 949i to come in from the U.S. Cant wait.  Well didn't make it out today but tomorrow is another day.
